    "title": [
      "[House Sovyn, Courtyard]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "Fragrant herbs and flowers grow under fruit trees around a small hillock where empaths and clerics see to those in need.  A fountain rests in the middle of the hillock where a crystal wind chime sways in the wind, hanging from a willow tree.  A large house, ordained with silver spires and twined ivy, is accented by a crystal tower on one side.  Double doors carved in rich pinewood give entrance to the house."
    ],
